item.title:
Shailene Woodley, Cara Delevingne & Noémie Merlant to star in a genre biopic of Patricia Highsmith.
It will reimagine the author’s life as a horror movie & focus on the period before she wrote The Talented Mr. Ripley, partly inspired by her doomed relationships with 2 women.
